description: Beachy Cream has been selling its surf-inspired certified organic ice cream sandwiches from its mobile cart since 2010. They are now introducing incredibly delicious innovative sandwiches, including:Key Lime Cowabunga (Key Lime Ice Cream between two Coconut Oatmeal Cookies)Ginger Wipeout (Candied Ginger Ice Cream, Molasses Spice Cookies)Strawberry Surfer Girl (Strawberry Balsamic Swirl between two Sugar Cookies)These tasty treats are served by none other than the Beachy Cream Girls: Retro-dressed beauties that carry these delightful ice cream treats on “cigarette trays.” It’s no wonder that this brilliant brand has exploded onto the beach scene!Jive on over and try a neat Beachy Cream frozen treat. It’s old-fashioned fun and flavorful dream come true.
name: Beachy Cream
